0.4 / 2012-05-12
- Allow random access in ItemEnumerator via #[]
- Rename "error queue" to "processing set", add timestamps, and allow iteration
through this set.
- Wire through a "descriptor" field to allow marking of items on the processing set
with who is processing them.
- Improve documentation.

0.3 / 2012-04-28:
- items were not actually being removed from the error queue. fix that.
- add #items for iterating over items for debugging purposes.
- add #size and #error_queue_size methods

